question: who is working in renewable energy?
query: SELECT ?name WHERE { { ?entity a <http://schema.org/Organization> . ?entity <http://schema.org/areaServed> <https://example.com/urn:impactarea:Energy> . ?entity <http://schema.org/name> ?name . } UNION { ?entity a <http://schema.org/Person> . ?entity <http://schema.org/knowsAbout> ?knowledge . FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(?knowledge), "energy")) . ?entity <http://schema.org/name> ?name . } FILTER (!STRSTARTS(STR(?entity), "_:")) }
